Ive dont everything to try and get it to work correctly and my conclusion is that its the game itself because other more intensive games work fine. Not going to stop me from playing it i just want the developers thoughts on it.

Love the game, played some last night and immediately decided to purchase the ad free version. I couldn't get the import/export to work, and the cloud save kept giving me an error. Not a huge deal because I wasnt very far, but I had to restart. Suggestion: to my understanding this game requires you to be online?I work in areas with no signal very often, please consider removing that requirement for the paid version of the game. Really enjoy the artwork of the game. Simple but gets it done.
replyContent: Hey Reese, thanks so much for the review! With regards to offline mode, this will be very hard due to how the game is updated very regularly and it downloads the latest changes when loading. But it is something I am looking implementing in the future :)

content: In my opinion, this feels like RuneScape without having to walk 10 miles, this game may start slow, but once you start rolling, more and more things open up to you, each activity you will connect to another activity, allot of things are tied together. An idle game that deserves a 5 star rating, it's the fist time I bought the ad free version of the, because God damnit you guys deserve it.
The games skill system is a straight rip off of RuneScape
Great potential, can't wait to see what the finished product looks like.
Best bar filling simulator by far XD
The best game ever, i'm excited to see more and more skills and content!!!

I love how even the free versione was well monetized, game is great, but i have some suggestion that when we are shopping cash was always visible to see and also when ever we gather a resources tels us +1(101) so we know how much we have in our inventory instead of checking inventory all the time, overall great job devswell done, keep it up.
Its runescape. Simplified.
Great idle
Great Game
I don't normally leave reviews here on the app store, but I had to give this game top marks. It's the best idle game I've played by a mile. Well done to the devs
replyContent: Thanks so much for the kind words and support Peter, it means a lot!

content: This is an idle game that replicates osrs and is done beautifully. It also has no iap for progression, only to support the developer. Never played RuneScape? Not a problem either. The game is based on many mmo characteristics. You want to grind and level up but don't have time to spend waiting for travel or have a job irl? Then pick this up immediately.
There can be only one, Melvor Idle!!!! Seriously uninstall the other version when you purchase this. 5 stars. Tasty fruit mmmmm.Backup your saves!!!...
Exceptional game. If you ever enjoyed RuneScape this is definitely a game for you.
Fun game! I play mostly on browser, and bought the mobile app to support the creators :)
Great idle game based on Runescape. I mostly play on pc but it's nice being able to play mobile Aswell.
Truly amazing, i love idle games and familiar concepts. Runescape was awesome. I hope this devs game blows up

Question: So the game is great, but the combat UI is hard to work with. Are there plans to hide the Monster Container elements just like the player's? Or move the Loot Container up between the player and monster? It would be really great to see the player health bar, food, monster health bar, and loot all on the same screen.
Love it so far, big OSRS player and I started playing this on the side after I found out about it on Reddit today. Didn't mind paying for the app to show my support.
Love this game. The first event was really good. I would recommend!
Great
Just what I was looking for since the official runescape idle game shut down years ago
Great idle fun. Not pay to win
Really excellent Idle RPG game with a great community. Approximately monthly updates to not only add new content to be update the existing too keeps the whole game fresh.
Great idle game!
as a runescape fan this is the best idle game I've ever played hands down.

The simplicity of a truely idle game, yet enough immersive strategy to recreate the feeling of runescape while also much more manageable and accessible during work breaks. Must try for lovers of the genre, even the interface is very understandable with no instructions necessary and very pleasing to the eye. Very happy with the results after purchasing at random.
Really cool up and coming idle game. Super well made and unlike most other idle games. I will be playing this one for some time.
Highly recommend this game. Been playing on PC and wanted to support developer. Active developer that listens to feedback.
I've been addicted to this game ever since my boy told me about it. The Dev is super friendly and I had to throw some cash his way as soon as I heard this was on Android. Thanks for making this.

Old School Runescape but better in my opinion. You are doing exactly what you do in OSRS but without all the tedious things that come with it. If there was a 6th star, it would get it. Best idle/semi-idle game on mobile!
True idle game, lots of depth to it. Think Runescape, but as a text based idle game. Dev is repsonsive and listens to feedback via Discord. Keep up the great work!
This game has a lot to offer being in such an early build and is getting regular updates.
